descriptions: A settled nomad living on the edge of Appalachia.  I love to listen to music, spend time with my family, and play sports.  I'm lucky enough to write code for a living.  I'm often accused of having no "filter" as I tend to overshare.  I make beer on occasion and try to sample new beers whenever I can.
My musings, thoughts, and meanderings.  An eclectic mix of errata
